Ancient X Files: Series 2

History Documentary hosted by Chris Porter, published by National Geographic in 2012 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

Ancient X Files: Series 2
In the modern information age, you'd like to think you have all the knowledge in the world at your fingertips - yet some shocking secrets remain buried deep in the past. Join intrepid investigators in our brand new series Ancient X Files as they delve into some of mankind's most enduring mysteries.



4)  Sodom and Gomorrah 
Sodom And Gomorrah &amp; Voyinch Manuscript
Go in search of the infamous Biblical cities of sin supposedly destroyed by the wrath of God. Can they be found? Plus, British computer programmer Nick Pelling attempts to crack 'the most mysterious document in the world'.


